<h5 id="subject_40697">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;topic=5374.msg40697#msg40697" rel="nofollow">翻译问题</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_40697'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_40697'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #37 于:</strong> 2005-11-24, 周四 18:18:15 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_40697_quick_mod"></div>
